1. *Moraju* da se pridržavaju zakona. (They must abide by the law.)

2. Oni *moraju* da razmišljaju o svojoj budućnosti. (They must think about their future.)

3. *Moraju* da pokažu poštovanje prema drugima. (They must show respect to others.)

4. Da bi uspeli, oni *moraju* da rade mnogo. (In order to succeed, they must work hard.)

5. Oni *moraju* da se prilagode novim okolnostima. (They must adapt to the new circumstances.)